      Instructions
      ------------
      Copy the file to your child theme and put whatever you need from the 
      above inbetween the CDATA in the after tag.
      
      Full and Resposive contain complete sets also available in:
        head-nonresponsive
        head-responsive
        head-nonresponsive-gridless
        head-responsive-gridless
      
      Check the manner of concatenation in the gridless link href to see how to
      combine resources from the Base, Responsive and Non Responsive sections.
